OL,6,FPlymouth's MPs want to avoid the same
OL,7,Fthing happening in Keyham.
OL,9,FLuke Pollard, Labour MP for Plymouth
OL,10,FSutton and Devonport, said: "People
OL,11,Fshould have certainty that if they're
OL,12,Finsured, insurance companies can't use
OL,13,Fthe loophole that those bombs were
OL,14,Fdropped in an act of war to avoid
OL,15,Fpeople being paid out.
