OL,6,F"It's about peace of mind for people.
OL,7,FA simple change that we know in
OL,8,FPlymouth and in Exeter will make a big
OL,9,Fdifference. Should this happen again.
OL,10,FJohnny Mercer, Conservative for
OL,11,FPlymouth Moor View, said: "These
OL,12,Fresidents are not unreasonable people.
OL,13,FThey understand that this could take
OL,14,Ftime, but they want to see a pathway,
OL,15,Fthey want to see a vision
OL,17,F"They want to see how their lives are
